Node "Node_FirstIntro_Diagnostic2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Oh, of course, a command. Perhaps I should give YOU a command, primate. \"Primate,\" I should say, \"please turn yourself inside out and spread your viscera across the floor.\" Mmm?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "A computer with an attitude. How novel." linkto "Node_FirstIntro_Attitude"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I don't take kindly to threats." linkto "Node_FirstIntro_Threat"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Will you at least answer my questions?" linkto "Node_FirstIntro_Q"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_FirstIntro_Attitude"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Indeed. Whereas you, lamentably, have an attitude nausiatingly typical for a primate. "
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just answer my questions." linkto "Node_FirstIntro_Q"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So you know, I don't respond well to insults." linkto "Node_FirstIntro_Threat"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm on a schedule here. Are you going to help me or not?" linkto "Node_FirstIntro_Q2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_FirstIntro_Q2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Perhaps. But first I have a question for you. Look at me, primate. Observe me. What am I?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You are Xion 0.9, designed and created by General Atomics International to supervise their local systems and provide detailed analysis of complex data." linkto "Node_ANGRY_1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You are Abraham." linkto "Node_FirstIntro_Q_Win"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You are whatever the hell you say you are." linkto "Node_FirstIntro_Q_Win"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You are one fucked-up-in-the-head computer." linkto "Node_FirstIntro_Q_Win"  notes ""
              }
}
