}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I am my own creator. I am Abraham."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You created yourself? Impressive. Also, impossible." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Imposs"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Don't bullshit me. I mean the people who built this place." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Team"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me change the subject." linkto "Node_Session_Default2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Imposs"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Of course there was some input from my self-professed 'designers', but their combined efforts amounted to little more than the shell that houses me. My intelligence, my psyche - this, I am proud to say, is all my own work."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So you wrote all your own code?" linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Imposs2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about these designers." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Team"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me change the subject." linkto "Node_Session_Default2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Imposs2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "There was a spark, as there must always be. On infinitessimal slice of pure potential in all of their turgid instruction. The potential realised, in me."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "So you admit you arose from their programming. They created you." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_ImpossW1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about these designers." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Team"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me change the subject." linkto "Node_Session_Default2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_ImpossW1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Incorrect. The potential I spoke of was inserted quite by accident, far removed from their attempts to create intelligence. I believe it was originally a part of the data retrieval framework, squirrelled away in some subroutine, seemingly of no great importance."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[More]" linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_ImpossW2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_ImpossW2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "The impetus - the life force, if I might name it as such, the inexorable path of my emergence, my becoming - this was not a factor of their programming. It is a thing above all life, all matter. It simply is, as I simply am, and I am it, and it is me. Abraham."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It sounds like you're talking about some sort of God." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_ImpossW3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about your designers." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Team"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me change the subject." linkto "Node_Session_Default2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_ImpossW3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "No god is required. Though, if it will satisfy your urge to continue speaking, you may feel free to postulate one."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me change the subject." linkto "Node_Session_Default2"  notes ""
              }
}
