Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Blaine"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Blaine, of course. A dead fool.  A fat-headed maladroit with the teremerity to list me with the sordid patents on his resume. His expression upon expiration is among the fondest of my recollections."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You mean you watched him die?" linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Blaine2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about someone else." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Team2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Blaine2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "But of course, primate. I pay very close attention to what I'm doing."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You killed him? Why?" linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Blaine3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about someone else." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Team2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Blaine3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Dr Blaine and I had differences of opinion. He, the incomprehensibly inept egoist, thought that 'Xion' would be a suitable catachresis with which to sell me to the world. I prohibited the marketing of my intelligence under any name."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You killed him over a name?" linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Blaine4"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Blaine4"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I insinuated that, should he not reverse his position, my admonition would assume a lethal nature. He doubted my resolve. By his own word, so it was done."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sounds like he had it coming." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Blaine5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're a murderer, Abraham, any way you slice it." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Blaine6"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Don't you think that was a little extreme?" linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Blaine6"  notes ""
              }
}
