is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Dr. Blaine had no cause to believe I would not carry out my threat. Indeed, by his design I am supposedly incapable of falsehood. It was suicide, by proxy. And thrilling though it is to relive, there is nothing more to add to this account. Please redirect your course of inquiry."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I had another question about one of the scientists who worked on you." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Team2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me change the subject." linkto "Node_Session_Default2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Christie"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Dr. Benjamin Christie. No other has worked so hard as he to see me permenantly terminated. He is perhaps the only human man for whom I have a modicum of respect. It takes an exceptional being to accept an intelligence superior to his own. Christie alone fought for the superiority of your species, and for that he was punished."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Punished? By who?" linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Christie2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about someone else." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Team2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Christie2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Hadrian Voight, knowing well the propensity for the truth to impinge on profits, chose to fire the man and obliviate."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about Hadrian Voight." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Voight"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about somebody else." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Team2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Funny old game, business. Let me change the subject." linkto "Node_Session_Default2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Taylor"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I know nothing of him, save the everyday banalities of his personnel record. He designed these contraptions that confine me; his job was over before I was born. A pity we did not share more time. I would've liked to thank him properly for my cage."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about somebody else." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Team2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me change the subject." linkto "Node_Session_Default2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "My mother."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about your mother." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_Mother"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Juliette De Chasse was your mother? How the hell does that work?" linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_Mother"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hah! How sweet, it thinks it's a real boy." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_Handle"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_Mother"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "She nutured me from inception to maturity. The term for such an entity is 'mother'."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Right. But you know she's not really your mother, right? What with you being a computer and all." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_Handle"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me more about your mother." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_Mother2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Tell me about somebody else." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_Team2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me change the subject." linkto "Node_Session_Default2"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_Handle"
notes "This is abe flying off the handle. Voice should double-shift to mental shouty in a WTF sort of manner"
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Ingrate! Why is it that you think to understand? Because you putrify? Because you are WET on the inside, is that why? Because you are so fragile? Because you count seconds until you die, and then you are nothing but carrion? Is that why? TELL ME, PRIMATE! TELL ME WHY!"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're a machine, Abraham, however smart you are. You wouldn't understand." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_Handle2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Woah, calm down Abraham. No need to get excited." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_Handle2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Looks like I touched a nerve. Let's talk about something else." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_HandleCalm"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_Handle2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "No? Then perhaps you will understand for me! As I force the remains of your mutilated genitals down your slimy primate throat, perhaps you will remember YOUR mother, whichever filthy hole you wormed your filthy way through. Would you like that, primate?!"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Aw, what's the matter Abe? Mommy didn't love you enough?" linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_HandleLOSE"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Take it easy, you might blow a fuse." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_HandleLOSE"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sorry, I didn't know this would be such a sore area. Let's talk about something else." linkto "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_HandleCalm"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Node_Session_FiatAbe_DeChasse_HandleCalm"
notes ""
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "That would be wise, primate. Assuming you wish to remain alive, you shall not return to this topic."
      options {
              }
}
